## What This Module Does

This module ports the "Depth Acid Fractal" datamosh effect from VJlive-2. It applies a combination of extreme visual processing based on depth:
- Depth-modulated Julia set fractals
- Prismatic RGB splitting
- Sabattier effect (solarization/inversion)
- Cross-processing and neon film burns
- Depth-controlled radial zoom blur

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- It does NOT rely on any third-party fractal libraries; it computes the Julia set purely via GLSL fragment shaders.
- It does NOT perform optical flow or motion estimation.

